HEADWORD: insistency
<hw>insistency</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>the state of urgently demanding
notice or attention; insistence.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> imperativeness, insistence, press,
pressure.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>the quality of not being ignorable.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> imperativeness, insistence.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

